    &lt;TFOOT&gt;
         &lt;TR&gt; ...footer information...
    &lt;/TFOOT&gt;
    &lt;TBODY&gt;
         &lt;TR&gt; ...first row of block one data...
         &lt;TR&gt; ...second row of block one data...
    &lt;/TBODY&gt;
    &lt;TBODY&gt;
         &lt;TR&gt; ...first row of block two data...
         &lt;TR&gt; ...second row of block two data...
